    "This involves, first, creative ideas about future organizational structures other than the plethora of hierarchical models in place.",
    "In this respect, the terms \"overarchy\" and \"holarchy\" provide useful points of departure for a scale from a total separation via the interaction between different agencies or entities to their overlap and optimal connection through complete integration.",
